This directory contains base class templates for classes that are used
in directories src/rpc and src/rpg to implement SCFT and PS-FTS 
calculations for methods that use real fields and periodic boundary
conditions. 

Classes:

  Prdc::Rl::System          - base for (Rpc|Rpg)::System
  Prdc::Rl::SystemConstRef  - base for (Rpc|Rpg)::System
  Prdc::Rl::Domain          - base class for (Rpc|Rpg)::Domain
  Prdc::Rl::FieldIo         - base class for (Rpc|Rpg)::FieldIo
  Prdc::Rl::WFields         - base class for (Rpc|Rpg)::WFields 
  Prdc::Rl::CFields         - base class for (Rpc|Rpg)::CFields 
  Prdc::Rl::Mask            - base class for (Rpc|Rpg)::Mask

Files that define global function templates:

  fieldIoUtil.h    - functions used in FieldIoReal
  fieldArrayUtil.h - utilities field containers
    
